<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pink Travel - Start</title>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #FFF5F8; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .bilet {
            background: white; border: 2px solid #FF69B4; max-width: 700px; margin: 50px auto;
            position: relative; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px #FFB6C1; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header-bilet { background: #FF69B4; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .titlu-mare { font-size: 3em; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 5px; }
        .continut { padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .foto-polaroid {
            background: white; padding: 10px 10px 30px 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transform: rotate(-3deg);
            display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn-aventura {
            display: inline-block; padding: 15px 25px; margin: 10px; border: 2px solid #FF69B4;
            color: #FF69B4; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s; text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .btn-aventura:hover { background: #FF69B4; color: white; transform: scale(1.05); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bilet">
        <div class="header-bilet">
            <h1 class="titlu-mare">Pink Travel</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="continut">
            <p>Gata de plecare?</p>
            
            <div class="foto-polaroid">
                <img src="/insula.jpg" alt="Destinatie" width="300">
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #888; font-family: cursive;">Vedere de vis...</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="/login" class="btn-aventura">Check-in (Login)</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn-aventura">Pasaport Nou (Register)</a>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #aaa;">Am ales acest proiect pentru ca imi plac calatoriile.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>